Traditional Automation

1. Identify Automation scenarios
2. manual testcases - > automation test scripts
      |->excel, CSV, test management tools like JIRA, ALM, Qtest
3. write testcases in BDD cucumber feature file format

Cucumber BDD plugin in IDE
1. feature file with file extension of <filename>.feature

Feature: .........feature name......
 Description of feature

 scenario :  --> your testcase

    Given - precondition
    When - all user actions
    Then - verification./ validation
    And - conjunction word to link more than one when/ then statement
    But - negative positives


    1. feature file creation - DOne
    2. Create the runner file - cucumber configuration - Done
            |-> Options
                    |-> feature location*
                    |-> Glue*
                    |-> tags
                    |-> plugin
    3. Step Definition - Done
    4. PageFactory - Done
